data.description: Welcome to this beautiful 3 bedroom, 2 bath home, ideally located in the Wood Hollow Estates. Home features tile floors, quartz countertops, high ceilings, remodeled bathrooms and two living areas (one of which is being used as a personal Gym). This Beauty has a **NEW Roof (2 yrs old), NEW AC, and NEW water Heater plus conveying Appliances with a NEW Stove and NEW Microwave Oven. The Spacious back yard and Patio offers plenty of space for your friends and family weekend BBQ's. In addition the back yard encompasses a Newly Constructed Shed.    Located just minutes away from H-E-B Grocery, Shopping Centers, and Restaurants. Don't miss out on this fantastic opportunity to live in the Center of Everything. Schedule your showing today!
